Follower,creators choice. This follower will show up in same location as DezLyn, I would untic DezLyn  if one giant is all you are wanting. She has the best perks out of the rest of my followers.

File Ohm, the update is a bit stronger than MissNayLyn but same body face. Still works well with near all mods.1.5 scale. lil smaller than a giant a lil bit bigger than a troll. MissNayLyn is made  from Aranea Ienith. She can be found at the Shrine of Azura, near Winterhold. If on location wait one HR , and she will appear.
